'''Hayden Glacier''' is located in the US state of [[Oregon]]. The glacier is situated in the [[Cascade Range]] at an elevation between {{convert|8800|and|7800|ft}}. It is to the northeast of [[Three Sisters (Oregon)|Middle Sister]] and south of North Sister, both of which are extinct volcanoes.<ref name=topo>{{Cite map|publisher=TopoQwest (United States Geological Survey Maps)|title=North Sister, OR|url=http://www.topoquest.com/map.php?lat=44.15039&lon=-121.77615&datum=nad83&zoom=4|accessdate=2012-07-15}}</ref>

